    "xrefs": [
      {
        "r": "EPH.3.1",
        "v": 5
      },
      {
        "r": "PHM.1.9",
        "v": 5
      },
      {
        "r": "COL.1.1",
        "v": 5
      },
      {
        "r": "PHP.2.25",
        "v": 5
      },
      {
        "r": "1CO.3.9",
        "v": 4
      },
      {
        "r": "PHP.4.3",
        "v": 3
      },
      {
        "r": "2CO.1.1",
        "v": 3
      },
      {
        "r": "COL.4.11",
        "v": 3
      },
      {
        "r": "2TI.1.8",
        "v": 3
      },
      {
        "r": "1TH.3.2",
        "v": 3
      },
      {
        "r": "EPH.4.1",
        "v": 3
      },
      {
        "r": "PHM.1.24",
        "v": 2
      },
      {
        "r": "EPH.6.20",
        "v": 2
      },
      {
        "r": "2TH.1.1",
        "v": 2
      }
    ],
    "section": null
  },
  "PHM.1.2": {
    "text": "also to Apphia our sister and Archippus our fellow soldier—and to the church that meets in your home:",
    "footnotes": [],
    "xrefs": [
      {
        "r": "PHP.2.25",
        "v": 7
      },
      {
        "r": "COL.4.17",
        "v": 6
      },
      {
        "r": "ROM.16.5",
        "v": 6
      },
      {
        "r": "COL.4.15",
        "v": 4
      },
      {
        "r": "2TI.2.3-4",
        "v": 3
      },
      {
        "r": "1CO.16.19",
        "v": 3
      }
    ],
    "section": null
  },
  "PHM.1.3": {
    "text": "Grace and peace to you from God our Father and the Lord Jesus Christ.",
    "footnotes": [
      {
        "marker": "#",
        "text": "The Greek is plural; also in verses 22 and 25; elsewhere in this letter “you” is singular."
      }
    ],
    "xrefs": [
      {
        "r": "ROM.1.7",
        "v": 5
      },
      {
        "r": "EPH.1.2",
        "v": 4
      },
      {
        "r": "2CO.13.14",
        "v": 3
      }
    ],
    "section": null
  },
  "PHM.1.4": {
    "text": "I always thank my God as I remember you in my prayers,",
    "footnotes": [],
    "xrefs": [
      {
        "r": "ROM.1.8",
        "v": 7
      },
      {
        "r": "EPH.1.16",
        "v": 6
      },
      {
        "r": "COL.1.3",
        "v": 5
      },
      {
        "r": "PHP.1.3",
        "v": 5
      },
      {
        "r": "2TH.1.3",
        "v": 4
      },
      {
        "r": "1TH.1.2",
        "v": 4
      },
      {
        "r": "2TI.1.3",
        "v": 2
      }
    ],
    "section": "Thanksgiving and Prayer"
  },
  "PHM.1.5": {
    "text": "because I hear about your love for all his holy people and your faith in the Lord Jesus.",
    "footnotes": [],
    "xrefs": [
      {
        "r": "COL.1.4",
        "v": 10
      },
      {
        "r": "EPH.1.15",
        "v": 7
      },
      {
        "r": "PSA.16.3",
        "v": 3
      },
      {
        "r": "1CO.16.1",
        "v": 3
      },
      {
        "r": "1JN.5.1-2",
        "v": 3
      },
      {
        "r": "1JN.3.23",
        "v": 2
      },
      {
        "r": "PHM.1.7",
        "v": 2
      },
      {
        "r": "GAL.5.6",
        "v": 2
      },
      {
        "r": "ROM.15.25-26",
        "v": 2
      },
      {
        "r": "ROM.12.13",
        "v": 2
      },
      {
        "r": "ACT.9.39-41",
        "v": 1
      }
    ],
    "section": null
  },
  "PHM.1.6": {
    "text": "I pray that your partnership with us in the faith may be effective in deepening your understanding of every good thing we share for the sake of Christ.",
    "footnotes": [],
    "xrefs": [
      {
        "r": "2PE.1.8",
        "v": 13
      },
      {
        "r": "PHP.1.9-11",
        "v": 13
      },
      {
        "r": "COL.1.9",
        "v": 8
      },
      {
        "r": "1PE.1.5-8",
        "v": 5
      },
      {
        "r": "MAT.5.16",
        "v": 5
      },
      {
        "r": "TIT.3.14",
        "v": 4
      },
      {
        "r": "2CO.9.12-14",
        "v": 4
      },
      {
        "r": "1PE.2.12",
        "v": 4
      },
      {
        "r": "JAS.2.17",
        "v": 4
      },
      {
        "r": "JAS.2.14",
        "v": 4
      },
      {
        "r": "HEB.6.10",
        "v": 3
      },
      {
        "r": "1CO.14.25",
        "v": 3
      },
      {
        "r": "PHP.4.8",
        "v": 3
      },
      {
        "r": "1PE.3.16",
        "v": 3
      },
      {
        "r": "1PE.3.1",
        "v": 2
      }
    ],
    "section": null
  },
  "PHM.1.7": {
    "text": "Your love has given me great joy and encouragement, because you, brother, have refreshed the hearts of the Lord’s people.",
    "footnotes": [],
    "xrefs": [
      {
        "r": "2CO.7.13",
        "v": 10
      },
      {
        "r": "1TH.3.9",
        "v": 6
      },
      {
        "r": "2CO.7.4",
        "v": 6
      },
      {
        "r": "PHM.1.20",
        "v": 5
      },
      {
        "r": "3JN.1.3-6",
        "v": 5
      },
      {
        "r": "1TH.2.19",
        "v": 5
      },
      {
        "r": "2JN.1.4",
        "v": 4
      },
      {
        "r": "2TI.1.16",
        "v": 4
      },
      {
        "r": "1TH.1.3",
        "v": 2
      },
      {
        "r": "1TH.2.13",
        "v": 2
      }
    ],
    "section": null
  },
  "PHM.1.8": {
    "text": "Therefore, although in Christ I could be bold and order you to do what you ought to do,",
    "footnotes": [],
    "xrefs": [
      {
        "r": "1TH.2.6",
        "v": 8
      },
      {
        "r": "2CO.10.8",
        "v": 4
      },
      {
        "r": "2CO.3.12",
        "v": 3
      },
      {
        "r": "EPH.5.4",
        "v": 2
      },
      {
        "r": "2CO.10.1-2",
        "v": 2
      },
      {
        "r": "1TH.2.2",
        "v": 2
      },
      {
        "r": "2CO.11.21",
        "v": 2
      }
    ],
    "section": "Paul’s Plea for Onesimus"
  },
  "PHM.1.9": {
    "text": "yet I prefer to appeal to you on the basis of love. It is as none other than Paul—an old man and now also a prisoner of Christ Jesus—",
    "footnotes": [],
    "xrefs": [
      {
        "r": "EPH.4.1",
        "v": 4
      },
      {
        "r": "ROM.12.1",
        "v": 4
      },
      {
        "r": "2CO.5.20",
        "v": 4
      },
      {
        "r": "EPH.3.1",
        "v": 3
      },
      {
        "r": "PHM.1.1-25",
        "v": 2
      },
      {
        "r": "1PE.2.11",
        "v": 1
      },
      {
        "r": "ISA.46.4",
        "v": 1
      },
      {
        "r": "PSA.71.9",
        "v": 1
      },
      {
        "r": "PRO.16.31",
        "v": 1
      },
      {
        "r": "HEB.13.19",
        "v": 1
      },
      {
        "r": "2CO.6.1",
        "v": 1
      },
      {
        "r": "PSA.71.18",
        "v": 1
      }
    ],
    "section": null
  },
  "PHM.1.10": {
    "text": "that I appeal to you for my son Onesimus, who became my son while I was in chains.",
    "footnotes": [
      {
        "marker": "#",
        "text": "means"
      }
    ],
    "xrefs": [
      {
        "r": "COL.4.9",
        "v": 9
      },
      {
        "r": "1CO.4.15",
        "v": 8
      },
      {
        "r": "GAL.4.19",
        "v": 7
      },
      {
        "r": "1TI.1.2",
        "v": 7
      },
      {
        "r": "TIT.1.4",
        "v": 6
      },
      {
        "r": "2SA.19.37-38",
        "v": 5
      },
      {
        "r": "2SA.18.5",
        "v": 4
      },
      {
        "r": "2SA.9.1-7",
        "v": 4
      },
      {
        "r": "MRK.9.17",
        "v": 3
      }
    ],
    "section": null
  },
  "PHM.1.11": {
    "text": "Formerly he was useless to you, but now he has become useful both to you and to me.",
    "footnotes": [],
    "xrefs": [
      {
        "r": "2TI.4.11",
        "v": 8
      },
      {
        "r": "JOB.30.1-2",
        "v": 6
      },
      {
        "r": "LUK.15.32",
        "v": 5
      },
      {
        "r": "1PE.2.10",
        "v": 5
      },
      {
        "r": "LUK.17.10",
        "v": 4
      },
      {
        "r": "ROM.3.12",
        "v": 4
      },
      {
        "r": "MAT.25.30",
        "v": 4
      },
      {
        "r": "LUK.15.24",
        "v": 3
      }
    ],
    "section": null
  },
  "PHM.1.12": {
    "text": "I am sending him—who is my very heart—back to you.",
    "footnotes": [],
    "xrefs": [
      {
        "r": "MAT.6.14-15",
        "v": 4
      },
      {
        "r": "MAT.18.21-35",
        "v": 3
      },
      {
        "r": "JER.31.20",
        "v": 3
      },
      {
        "r": "EPH.4.32",
        "v": 3
      },
      {
        "r": "MRK.11.25",
        "v": 3
      },
      {
        "r": "LUK.15.20",
        "v": 3
      },
      {
        "r": "2SA.16.11",
        "v": 2
      },
      {
        "r": "DEU.13.6",
        "v": 2
      }
    ],
    "section": null
  },
  "PHM.1.13": {
    "text": "I would have liked to keep him with me so that he could take your place in helping me while I am in chains for the gospel.",
    "footnotes": [],
    "xrefs": [
      {
        "r": "PHP.1.7",
        "v": 4
      },
      {
        "r": "EPH.3.1",
        "v": 4
      },
      {
        "r": "1CO.16.17",
        "v": 3
      },
      {
        "r": "PHP.2.30",
        "v": 2
      },
      {
        "r": "EPH.4.1",
        "v": 2
      },
      {
        "r": "PHM.1.1",
        "v": 2
      }
    ],
    "section": null
  },
  "PHM.1.14": {
    "text": "But I did not want to do anything without your consent, so that any favor you do would not seem forced but would be voluntary.",
    "footnotes": [],
    "xrefs": [
      {
        "r": "2CO.9.7",
        "v": 8
      },
      {
        "r": "1PE.5.2-3",
        "v": 3
      },
      {
        "r": "1CH.29.17",
        "v": 3
      },
      {
        "r": "PHM.1.8-9",
        "v": 2
      },
      {
        "r": "1CO.9.17",
        "v": 2
      },
      {
        "r": "2CO.8.12",
        "v": 2
      },
      {
        "r": "2CO.9.5",
        "v": 2
      },
      {
        "r": "2CO.1.24",
        "v": 1
      },
      {
        "r": "PSA.110.3",
        "v": 1
      }
    ],
    "section": null
  },
  "PHM.1.15": {
    "text": "Perhaps the reason he was separated from you for a little while was that you might have him back forever—",
    "footnotes": [],
    "xrefs": [
      {
        "r": "GEN.50.20",
        "v": 7
      },
      {
        "r": "GEN.45.5-8",
        "v": 4
      },
      {
        "r": "ISA.20.6",
        "v": 2
      },
      {
        "r": "ACT.4.28",
        "v": 1
      }
    ],
    "section": null
  },
  "PHM.1.16": {
    "text": "no longer as a slave, but better than a slave, as a dear brother. He is very dear to me but even dearer to you, both as a fellow man and as a brother in the Lord.",
    "footnotes": [],
    "xrefs": [
      {
        "r": "COL.3.22",
        "v": 6
      },
      {
        "r": "MAT.23.8",
        "v": 6
      },
      {
        "r": "1TI.6.2",
        "v": 5
      },
      {
        "r": "1CO.7.22",
        "v": 5
      },
      {
        "r": "EPH.6.5-7",
        "v": 4
      },
      {
        "r": "1PE.1.22-23",
        "v": 3
      },
      {
        "r": "ACT.9.17",
        "v": 2
      },
      {
        "r": "HEB.3.1",
        "v": 2
      },
      {
        "r": "GAL.4.28-29",
        "v": 2
      },
      {
        "r": "1JN.5.1",
        "v": 1
      }
    ],
    "section": null
  },
  "PHM.1.17": {
    "text": "So if you consider me a partner, welcome him as you would welcome me.",
    "footnotes": [],
    "xrefs": [
      {
        "r": "2CO.8.23",
        "v": 8
      },
      {
        "r": "MAT.10.40",
        "v": 6
      },
      {
        "r": "PHM.1.12",
        "v": 4
      },
      {
        "r": "MAT.18.5",
        "v": 3
      },
      {
        "r": "EPH.3.6",
        "v": 2
      },
      {
        "r": "JAS.2.5",
        "v": 2
      },
      {
        "r": "HEB.3.1",
        "v": 2
      },
      {
        "r": "MAT.12.48-50",
        "v": 2
      },
      {
        "r": "ACT.16.15",
        "v": 2
      },
      {
        "r": "MAT.25.40",
        "v": 2
      },
      {
        "r": "1TI.6.2",
        "v": 1
      },
      {
        "r": "HEB.3.14",
        "v": 1
      },
      {
        "r": "PHP.1.7",
        "v": 1
      },
      {
        "r": "1PE.5.1",
        "v": 1
      },
      {
        "r": "1JN.1.3",
        "v": 1
      },
      {
        "r": "PHM.1.10",
        "v": 1
      }
    ],
    "section": null
  },
  "PHM.1.18": {
    "text": "If he has done you any wrong or owes you anything, charge it to me.",
    "footnotes": [],
    "xrefs": [
      {
        "r": "ISA.53.4-7",
        "v": 7
      }
    ],
    "section": null
  },
  "PHM.1.19": {
    "text": "I, Paul, am writing this with my own hand. I will pay it back—not to mention that you owe me your very self.",
    "footnotes": [],
    "xrefs": [
      {
        "r": "GAL.6.11",
        "v": 4
      },
      {
        "r": "GAL.5.2",
        "v": 3
      },
      {
        "r": "1CO.16.21-22",
        "v": 3
      },
      {
        "r": "JAS.5.19-20",
        "v": 2
      },
      {
        "r": "1CO.4.15",
        "v": 2
      },
      {
        "r": "1CO.9.1-2",
        "v": 2
      },
      {
        "r": "2CO.3.2",
        "v": 1
      },
      {
        "r": "TIT.1.4",
        "v": 1
      },
      {
        "r": "1TI.1.2",
        "v": 1
      }
    ],
    "section": null
  },
